Get free icons in Material Filled design style

Our consistent Material Filled icon pack follows the Material guidelines from Google, including the latest icon themes ( filled, outlined , rounded , two-tone, and sharp versions for each icon).

  • All themes are pixel-perfect at 2424 pixels.
  • These system icons cover a variety of common actions, files, devices, objects, and directories.

Download free Material Filled icons in different themes for your Android UI design. The graphics are available in both PNG and vector.
